node_2.subject: John Miller
node_2.description: This is John Miller's plan for Friday December 01: wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, breakfast from 7:00 am to 8:00 am, work as a security monitor from 8:00 am to 4:00 pm, lunch from 12:00 pm to 1:00 pm, take a short rest break from 1:00 pm to 2:00 pm, resume work from 2:00 pm to 4:00 pm, watch TV from 7:00 pm to 8:00 pm, and.
